for questioning?

18:40.590 --> 18:42.340 line:80%
No rush. I know what I'm doing.

18:42.440 --> 18:44.000 line:80%
Let's go check on that survivor first.

18:44.000 --> 18:44.310 line:80%
Yes,

18:44.310 --> 18:44.870 line:80%
My Lord.
